        "template--15839347146933__ceda7a35-055b-4054-a92e-18cb4417b5a7-168788011091c5710b-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Here at Kitsch, creating exceptional beauty products is just the beginning. <strong>We're on a mission to make a difference<\/strong>. With 4ocean, we've found a partner who shares our commitment to a cleaner, healthier planet. <br\/><br\/><\/p><p>Through our partnership, <strong>for every shampoo or conditioner bar you purchase, 4ocean will pull the equivalent of 1 shampoo bottle worth of plastic from our oceans and coastlines<\/strong>. With billions of pounds of plastic entering the ocean each year, every bar makes a difference. <\/p>",
            "text_font": "font-default",
            "font_size": 16,
            "text_align": "text-center",
            "font_size_mobile": 16,
            "text_align_mobile": "text-left"
          }
        }
      },
