        "e4770915-fed3-46b4-8700-5eda4dec6b0e": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>With our best-selling <strong>Bottle-Free Beauty® <\/strong>Bars<strong> <\/strong>we're making sustainability effortless. When you choose <strong>Kitsch<\/strong>, you're not just choosing high-quality beauty products – you're choosing a brand that takes on the burden of sustainability, for you. <br\/><br\/>We're committed to reducing plastic packaging, using recycled materials, and fostering partnerships like the one we have with <strong>4ocean<\/strong>. Every purchase you make contributes to our shared goal of cleaner oceans & coastlines, proving that even small decisions in your beauty routine can lead to big impacts around the world. <br\/><br\/>Transform your routine knowing each use is a step towards a more sustainable world.<\/p>",
            "text_font": "font-default",
            "font_size": 16,
            "text_align": "text-center",
            "font_size_mobile": 16,
            "text_align_mobile": "text-left"
          }
