        "5c9462f2-6571-4257-91b7-b8c2d1254c3a": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Ready to Make Waves?<\/strong><br\/><br\/>We're just at the beginning of this journey and we'd love for you to join us. There's a myriad of ways to get involved and support our mission. <br\/><br\/>Share the news of our partnership, shop our sustainable <strong>Bottle-Free Beauty®<\/strong> Bars*, or simply spread the word about the importance of ocean conservation. Every action counts. <br\/><br\/><strong>Let's make waves together.<\/strong><\/p><p>*Nine shampoo\/conditioner bars equal one pound of plastic removed from the oceans, rivers, and coastlines of the world.<\/p>",
